	<element name="Potion of Hill Giant Strength" type="Magic Item" source="Dungeon Master’s Guide 2024" id="ID_WOTC_DMG24_MAGIC_ITEM_POTION_OF_HILL_GIANT_STRENGTH">
		<description>
			<p>When you drink this potion, your Strength score changes to 21 for 1 hour. The potion has no effect on you if your Strength is equal to or greater than that score.</p>
			<p class="indent">This potion's transparent liquid has floating in it a sliver of fingernail from a hill giant.</p>
