			<p>When you drink this potion, you gain 10 Temporary Hit Points that last for 1 hour. For the same duration, you are under the effect of the Bless spell (no Concentration required).</p>
			<p class="indent">This potion's blue liquid bubbles and steams as if boiling.</p>
