	<element name="Potion of Poison" type="Magic Item" source="Dungeon Master’s Guide 2024" id="ID_WOTC_DMG24_MAGIC_ITEM_POTION_OF_POISON">
		<description>
			<p>This concoction looks, smells, and tastes like a Potion of Healing or another beneficial potion. However, it is actually poison masked by illusion magic. The <i>Identify</i> spell reveals its true nature.</p>
			<p class="indent">If you drink this potion, you take 4d6 Poison damage and must succeed on a DC 13 Constitution saving throw or have the Poisoned condition for 1 hour.</p>
		</description>
